<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN223">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>palarkkuniḻa lāki yulakamīk kūṟit</l>
<l>talaippō kaṉmaiyiṟ ciṟuvaḻi maṭaṅki</l>
<l>nilaipeṟu naṭuka lākiyak kaṇṇu</l>
<l>miṭaṅkoṭut taḷippa maṉṟa vuṭampō</l>
<l>ṭiṉṉuyir virumpuṅ kiḻamait</l>
<l>toṉṉaṭ puṭaiyār tammuḻaic celiṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Being shade for many, lauded by the world, (1)</l>
<l>bending over a little way in the absence of [total] destruction, (2)</l>
<l>also in the places where they have become upright hero stones (3)</l>
<l>they surely will provide a place, (4a-c)</l>
<l>– if, with a claim that desires sweet life along with the body (4df.) </l>
<l>those who feel old friendship go near them. (6)</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
